# SyllabiQ Frontend Rules

## Stack
- React 18, TypeScript, Vite 6, Tailwind v4, Radix UI, Motion (Framer Motion)

## API Client
- `src/lib/api.ts` — `postQuery`, `streamQuery`, `getSubjects`, `getTopics`, `getInstitutions`, `getDepartments`, `getDashboard`, `authSignup`, `authLogin`
- Base: `VITE_API_BASE` (default `http://localhost:8000/api`)
- Auth: `authHeader()` from `src/lib/auth.ts` — include for protected endpoints

## Paths
- Subject/topic: Use `/content/subjects` and `/content/subjects/{id}/topics` (not `/v1/subjects`)
- Query: `POST /v1/query` (relative to API_BASE)

## Components
- `src/app/components/` — UI; `ui/` for Radix primitives
- `AuthContext`, `DashboardContext` for shared state
- `ProtectedRoute` for auth-gated routes

## Accessibility
- WCAG 2.1 AA: contrast 4.5:1, keyboard nav, focus states, aria-labels
- Icons paired with text; semantic HTML

## Data
- Pass **UUIDs** for subject/topic to Chat; avoid display names in API calls
